WEBVTT

34:30.900 --> 34:32.610
He's moving away.

34:38.200 --> 34:40.910
I'm sorry, my love.

34:46.210 --> 34:47.820
Maybe this is a blessing.

34:48.010 --> 34:50.130
He asked me to go with him.

34:51.590 --> 34:52.880
Where?

35:04.560 --> 35:08.540
You can't, your family is here.

35:08.740 --> 35:10.920
Nothing's more important
than that.

35:11.120 --> 35:13.730
You never turn your back
on family.
